{"tid":2492605,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫院文職人員被指查閱個人資料被捕 涉警員和政治人物","createTime":"2021-04-17T08:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T09:20:32.000Z","uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"742e6c913e6d7b806858cd53a4905e69b5690fbf","tid":2492605,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:43:38.000Z","msg":"一名前醫院文職人員在去年2月至8月期間，於未有授權的情況下登入醫院電腦系統，查閱包括警務人員和政治人物在內的不同公眾人士個人資料。警方昨日（16日）以「有不誠實意圖而取用電腦」罪將其拘捕，被捕男子仍然被扣查，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，被查閱的個人資料並非病歷等敏感資料，本案受影響的人數仍在點算當中，其中包括有警務人員、藝人、政治人物，醫院高層人員和一些身份仍有待核實的人士。警方亦拒絕透露被捕人之前任職那一間醫院及從事的職位，只透露他是一名文職人員。<br />\n<br />\nRead more:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210417/7AYXNZWBMZAKNIEDE5MEP3A5JU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210417%2F7AYXNZWBMZAKNIEDE5MEP3A5JU%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL4pVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=35f4253f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210417%2F7AYXNZWBMZAKNIEDE5MEP3A5JU%2F&h=39bb32a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210417/7AYXNZWBMZAKNIEDE5MEP3A5JU/</a>"},{"pid":"16568607a42b5be435af830e8fcb04df31cd73e6","tid":2492605,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"犯法嘢難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419435dff7dbe5cad3358b62f84936403c28f40b","tid":2492605,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}